Amma matsalar tattalin arziki ta yi wa gwamnatin Joko barazana, wanda za a sake zabarsa a shekara mai zuwa.
Joko ma yana fuskantar matsaloli domin tashin hankali na addini a Indonesia, inda yawancin Musulmai suka amince da tsarin addini guda.
Fiye da mutane 1,000 aka kashe kuma dubban mutane suka gudu daga gidajensu yayin da 'yan tawaye na Kirista da na Musulmi suka yi yaƙi a kan tituna, suna amfani da wuƙaƙe, baka, da sauran makamai.
Kalli: Dan wasan Liverpool Daniel Sturridge ya ci kwallo mai karfi a wasan karshe da Chelsea ta yi.
Dan wasan ya ceci Liverpool daga barazanar shan kashi a Chelsea ta hanyar buga kwallo a minti 89 a ranar Asabar a filin wasa na Stamford Bridge da ke birnin London.
Sturridge da ke da nisan mil 30 daga burin Chelsea ya karbi kwallon daga Xherdan Shaqiri yayin da tawagarsa ta rage da ci 1-0.
Ya tura kwallon zuwa hagu sannan ya ja bam din da kwallon ta shiga cikin gefe wanda ya yi nesa da Sturridge.
Kwallan ya tashi sama kuma ya kai ga kusurwar sama ta hanyar tarun.
Kwallan ya wuce Kepa Arrizabalaga da ya yi tsalle kuma ya shiga cikin tarun.
"Na yi kokarin zama a wurin da kuma samun kwallon kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaqiri suna tura kwallon gaba sau da yawa, don haka na yi kokarin samun damar da zan iya", in ji Sturridge a cikin hira da LiverpoolFC.com.
"Na ga Kante yana zuwa, sai na buga ƙwallo sau ɗaya, sai na ja bam ɗin ba tare da na yi tunani ba".
Chelsea ta yi nasara da ci 1-0 a ƙarshen rabin wasan bayan da dan wasan Belgium Edin Hazard ya ci kwallo a minti na 25.
Dan wasan Chelsea ya kai kwallo Kovacic da diddige a tsakiyar filin wasan sannan ya juya ya shiga yankin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya ba abokinsa wanda ya mayar masa da ƙwallo a tsakiyar filin.
Sai ya ba da ƙwallon da ya bi Hazard a cikin akwatin kwallo a Liverpool.
Hazard ya yi saurin wucewa daga bayan Liverpool kuma ya buga ƙwallon da ke wucewa ta hanyar Alisson Becker kuma ya shiga raga a gefen da ke nesa da Hazard.
Liverpool za ta kara da Napoli a wasan rukuni na gasar zakarun Turai a ranar Laraba da karfe 3:00 na yamma a filin wasa na San Paolo a birnin Naples na Italiya.
Chelsea za ta kara da Videoton a gasar cin kofin zakarun Turai a ranar Alhamis da karfe uku na yamma a birnin Landan.
Mutane 832 sun mutu sanadiyyar tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Ma'aikatar kula da bala'i ta ce adadin mutanen da suka mutu a girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia ya kai 832.
Mutane da yawa sun kasance cikin rugujewar gine-gine da girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta lalata a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai tsawon kafa 20, mai magana da yawun kungiyar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho ya fada a wani taron manema labarai.
An rufe birnin Palu, da ke da mutane fiye da 380,000, da tarun gidaje da yawa da suka lalace.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 da ake zargi da kisan wata mata da wuka
An kaddamar da binciken kisan bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhead, Merseyside da safiyar yau.
An gano wata mata mai shekara 44 da raunuka a Grayson Mews da ke John Street da ƙarfe 7:55 na safe, kuma an kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 don zargin kisan.
'Yan sanda sun aririci mutanen yankin da suka ga ko kuma suka ji wani abu su zo.
'Bincike yana kan hanya,' in ji Sufeto Brian O'Hagan, 'amma ina roƙon duk wanda ke kusa da John Street a Birkenhead da ya ga ko ya ji wani abu mai ban mamaki ya gaya mana.
Ina kuma roƙon kowa, musamman direbobi na taksi, da za su iya ɗaukar hoton da ke cikin dashcam su yi magana da mu domin suna da kalmomin da za su taimaka wajen bincikenmu.'
