Akwai bambancin zafin jiki na kusan digiri 20 tsakanin Kansas City, Missouri, da Omaha, Nebraska, da kuma tsakanin St. Louis da Des Moines, Iowa.
A cikin 'yan kwanaki masu zuwa, zafin rana zai ƙara ƙaruwa.
