Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli gidan talabijin na shida inda wanda aka nada a Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh ya ba da shaidarsa a ranar Alhamis da Christine Blasey Ford wanda ya zarge shi da cin zarafin da aka yi masa a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, ana ci gaba da rikici na siyasa, yayin da kafofin watsa labarai ke katse shirin na yau da kullum a cikin wani ɓangare na ƙarshe na ranar Jumma'a: wani labari da Sanata Fl Flake na Arizona ya shirya don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda a kan waɗannan shari'o'in.
Ford ya gaya wa Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa ya tabbata da kashi 100 cewa Kavanaugh ya kama shi cikin maye kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinsa a wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidarsa mai kyau, ya ce yana da tabbaci cewa wannan bai faru ba.
Kamar dai fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka ga wannan ya faru, kamar yadda Nielsen ya ruwaito a ranar Jumma'a.
Kamfanin yana yin lissafin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Wasu ƙididdiga ba su kasance nan take a kan sauran hanyoyin sadarwar da suka nuna shirin ba, gami da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yana da matsala wajen samun adadin masu kallo a ofisoshi.
Don a kwatanta wannan, masu sauraro suna da girma kamar waɗanda suke wajen wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma a bikin sauke karatu.
Tashar Fox News Channel, wadda ke da mai magana da yawun da ya fi goyon bayan Kavanaughled, ta zarce dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa da masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a ranar sauraron, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ce ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
Jaridar Nielsen ta ce CBS tana da miliyan 3.1 da NBC miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da kuma CNN miliyan 2.52.
An ci gaba da ɗokin ganin yadda za a kammala wannan labarin.
Flake ya kasance da muhimmanci a abin da ya faru a ranar Jumma'a.
