Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawari a ranar Asabar a Tlatelolco Plaza cewa "ba za a taɓa yin amfani da sojoji ba wajen zaluntar mutanen Mexico".
Sojoji suka harbe ɗalibai da suke zanga-zanga a wannan filin wasa a ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, suka kashe mutane kusan 300 a lokacin da ƙungiyoyin 'yancin kai na makaranta suka kafa sansani a Latin Amirka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin taimaka wa matasa na Mexico ta hanyar ba da gudummawa ga waɗanda suke karatu da kuma buɗe jami'o'i masu yawa na jama'a kyauta.
Ya kuma ce rashin aikin yi da kuma rashin ilimi suna jawo matasa su shiga ƙungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda.
Gwamnatin Amirka za ta ƙara kuɗi don yin aiki kamar mutum
Yayin da kasar Sin ke samun ci gaba a fannin sarrafa kansa, dole ne Amirka ta ƙara kashe kuɗi a bincike a wannan fannin, in ji mai sana'a Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki da Google, Microsoft, da kuma Apple.
Wannan ya sa hukumomi da yawa a Amirka suka ce za su yi amfani da wannan na'urar, ko da yake ƙasar ba ta da tsarin da ya dace game da AI.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta fara wannan shirin ne a bara: kuma tana son ta zama kasa ta farko da ta fi amfani da fasahar nan a duniya nan da shekara ta 2030.
"Ƙara yawan kuɗin bincike zai zama mafari mai kyau, tun da yake dukan ƙasashe sun yi kasa da Amirka, kuma muna bukatar mu samu ayyuka masu ci gaba a fannin fasaha", in ji Lee.
Wannan ƙarin kuɗin zai iya ninka yiwuwar samun nasarar AI a Amurka, Lee ya gaya wa CNBC a cikin wata hira da aka yi da shi a wannan makon.
Lee, tare da wani ɗan littafin nan mai suna "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures ya wallafa a wannan watan, wanda ya zuba jari sosai a binciken da ake yi na na'urar sarrafa mutum a kasar Sin, Face++.
A shekarun 1980s, a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya kirkiro wani na'ura mai kwakwalwa da ya yi nasara a kan mai wasan kwaikwayo Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama shugaban bincike a Microsoft da kuma shugaban kamfanin Google a China.
Lee ya yi godiya ga kaddamar da gasar Robotics Challenge ta Hukumar Bincike ta Ƙasa ta Ƙasa kuma ya so ya san ranar da za a sake gudanar da gasar don taimakawa wajen gano masu fasaha na gaba.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amirka suna aiki tuƙuru don su sami lambar yabo daga gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin take karɓan mutane masu ilimi ba; kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da wasu kamfanoni suna karɓar ƙwararrun masana daga jami'o'i don su yi aiki a fannin AI a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce gyara da aka yi game da ƙaura zai iya taimaka wa Amirka ta ƙarfafa ayyukanta na AI.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da takardar izini ga waɗanda suka sami digiri na biyu a fannin fasaha.
Kasar Sin ta kaddamar da shirin bunkasa ayyukanta na kera motoci a watan Yuli na shekarar 2017.
Ƙungiyar Kimiyya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin ce take tallafa wa makarantun kimiyya kamar yadda ita da wasu hukumomin gwamnati suke tallafa wa masu bincike a Amirka, amma ba a koyar da 'yan China sosai ba, in ji Lee.
A farkon wannan shekara Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amirka ta kafa Cibiyar Sadarwa ta Artificial Intelligence, wadda za ta haɗa da masana'antu da kuma ma'aikata, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zaɓuɓɓuka na Sadarwa ta Artificial Intelligence.
Kuma a wannan watan DARPA ta sanar da zuba jari na dala biliyan biyu a shirin AI Next.
