Ƙungiyar Turai ta yi nasara da maki 10-6 a ranar ƙarshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Ƙungiyar Turai za ta yi farin ciki sosai a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder bayan ta ci Amurka a wasan kwallon kafa na hudu a ranar Asabar da maki 10-6.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun ja-goranci tawagar da Tiger Woods yake takawa, kuma nasarar da suka yi a wasan da aka yi a Le Golf National ya kai maki huɗu.
Ƙungiyar Turai da Thomas Bjorn ya koyar, suna son su sake lashe kofin da suka kasa kāre shekaru biyu da suka shige a filin wasa na Hazeltine, suka matsa wa Amirkawa a wasan su na safe na ƙwallo huɗu, bisa tsarin 3-1.
Ƙungiyar Amirka ta yi nasara a wasanni biyu, amma ba ta hana su cin nasara ba.
Ƙungiyar da Jim Furyk ya koyar tana bukatar maki takwas a wasanni 12 da za a yi a ranar Lahadi don ta ci kofin.
Fleetwood ne dan wasan Turai na farko da ya fara wasa a gasar da ya ci maki hudu a jere, kuma ta hanyar wasan da suka yi a karshen mako, shi da Molinari wanda magoya bayansa suka kira "Molliwood" su ne 'yan wasa na biyu da suka ci maki hudu a wasanni hudu na farko a tarihin gasar Ryder.
Bayan da suka ci Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan ƙwallon ƙafa, sai suka ci Woods da Bryson Dechambeau da maki biyar da huɗu a kan tawagar Amirka.
Woods, wanda ya yi ƙoƙari ya yi nasara a wasanni biyu na ranar Asabar, ya nuna ƙarfin hali a wasu lokatai amma a yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 19 na wasanni 29 na ƙwallon ƙafa da kuma wasanni bakwai na wasa.
Justin Rose, ya yi hutu a wasan safe na hudu, sai ya yi wasa biyu tare da Henrik Stenson a wasan hudu kuma ya ci Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka da maki 2 da 1 - na farko da na uku a duniya.
A wannan rana mai sanyi a kudu maso yammacin Paris, ƙungiyar Turai ba ta wuce hanya mai tsabta ba.
