Mai wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya fusata da ra'ayin da ya saɓa wa ra'ayin namiji
Kit Harington wanda aka sani da yin faɗa da wuka a matsayin Jon Snow a wasan kwaikwayo na HBO Game of Thrones.
Amma ɗan wasan kwaikwayo, ɗan shekara 31, ya ƙi yarda da ra'ayin cewa jarumawa suna da matsayi, yana cewa irin waɗannan matsayi a kan kafofin watsa labarai suna nufin cewa matasa maza suna jin cewa dole ne su yi girma don a daraja su.
Da yake magana da jaridar Sunday Times Culture, Kit ta ce ta gaskata cewa 'wani abu ba daidai ba ne' kuma ta yi tambaya game da hanyoyin magance ra'ayin da ya sabawa maza a wannan zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri Rose Leslie, 'yar shekara 31, wadda take cikin shirin Game of Thrones, ta yarda cewa yana ganin 'da muhimmanci' ya shawo kan wannan yanayin.
'A yanzu ina mamakin kaina - ina muka kwashe su?' in ji shi.
'Menene muke koya wa maza yayin da suke girma, musamman a wannan yanayin?'
Kit ya gaskata cewa rediyo na iya zama wani abu da zai iya taimaka wajen ci gaba da wannan halin amma godiya ga wasu daga cikin masu ba da tallafinsa maza suna da halin kirki.
Ya ci gaba: 'Me aka haifa mutane da shi kuma menene aka koya musu?
Waɗanne abubuwa ne ake nunawa a talabijin da kuma a wasu wurare da suke sa yara maza su ga cewa wannan shi ne ainihin abin da ya kamata su kasance da shi?
Ina ganin wannan tambaya ce mai muhimmanci a yanzu - ta yaya za mu canja wannan?
Babu shakka akwai wani abu da ba daidai ba da samarin nan suke yi.'
A lokacin ziyarar ta kuma yarda cewa ba za ta yi wasa ba a Game of Thrones lokacin da wasan kwaikwayon ya ƙare a wasan kwaikwayo na safe, ta ce, 'ta gama da yaki da hawa jaki'.
Tun watan Nuwamba Kit ya shiga cikin sake fasalin fim din True West wanda Sam Shepard ya shirya wanda ya shafi 'yan fim da dan uwansa wanda ya yi fashi.
Jarumin ya ce ya ga cewa saduwa da matarsa Rose ita ce mafi kyawun abin da ya samu a Game of Thrones.
'Na sadu da matata a lokacin da nake yin fim, saboda haka na sami iyali na har abada da kuma rayuwata duka,' in ji shi.
Rose ita ce Ygritte, wadda take son Jon Snow, wanda sunansa na ainihi shi ne Kit, a wasan kwaikwayon da ya ci lambar yabo ta Emmy.
Sun yi bikin aurensu a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan iyayensu a Scotland.
HIV da AIDS: China ta sanar da karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 bisa ɗari
Ƙasar ta sanar da cewa adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya ƙaru da kashi 14 bisa ɗari.
Kusan mutane 820,000 ne ke da cutar a ƙasar, in ji ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya.
An samu halartar mutane 40,000 a kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin mutanen sun kamu da cutar ta wurin jima'i, kuma hakan ya kawo canji.
A dā, ana yaɗuwar ƙwayoyin cuta ta HIV a wasu wurare ta wurin jini.
Amma an rage yawan masu kamuwa da cutar HIV ta hanyar wannan hanyar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
A kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i ta fi yawa a tsakanin mutane da suke luwadi.
An kawar da dokokin da suka hana yin jima'i tsakanin mutane na jinsi ɗaya a ƙasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga masu yin jima'i tsakanin mutane ya ƙaru a ƙasar.
Domin halin duniya na ƙin yin jima'i, bincike ya nuna cewa kusan kashi 70 zuwa 90 na maza da suke yin jima'i da jinsi ɗaya suna yin aure da mata.
Yawancin kamuwa da cutar a irin wannan dangantaka ta shafi jima'i ne.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin ba da taimakon da ya dace don magance cutar HIV ga kowa.
