Wannan sakon ya bayyana a shafin yanar gizon Capitol Hill a ranar Alhamis bayan da wani wanda ba a san shi ba ya sanya shi a lokacin da ake zargin Brett Kavanaugh wanda aka nada a matsayin babban alkalin kotun da ya nemi fyade.
