Yayin da yawancin shugabannin jam'iyyar Republican suka amince da nadin Brett Kavanaugh a matsayin babban alkalin kotun Koli duk da cewa ana zargin Kavanaugh da yin fyade, masana sun ce hakan zai jawo matsala, musamman daga mata a zaɓen da ke tafe.
