Ba za a iya canja waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Grant Reeher, malamin ilimin siyasa a makarantar Maxwell da ke Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata hira da ya yi da jaridar The Hill a kan wani talifi da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa ci gaba da binciken FBI da dan majalisar Arizona Jeff Flake ke yi a lokacin hutu zai iya kawar da fushin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mace ba za ta taɓa mantawa da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za ta taɓa mantawa da shi ba gobe ko kuma a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai koyar da mata na ƙungiyar mata mai suna MoveOn a ranar Jumma'a, in ji rahoton jaridar Washington DC.
A safiyar ranar Jumma'a, masu zanga-zanga suna rera waƙar "November is Coming!" yayin da suke zanga-zanga a cikin harabar majalisa yayin da 'yan majalisa na jam'iyyar Republican suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, jaridar Mic ta ruwaito.
"Mutane ba za su ƙara son tsarin dimokiradiyya ba", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wanda ya ƙware a siyasa.
