Ko da yake ba a riga an bayyana hujjojin da Ford ya bayar game da zargin fyade da aka yi wa Kavanaugh ba, masana sun ce idan jam'iyyar Republican ta tabbatar da cewa an naɗa Kavanaugh, za a yi fushi sosai.
"Wannan ya nuna rashin daidaito na jam'iyyar GOP", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National, makon da ya gabata, in ji rahoton NBC.
Guy Cecil, darektan da ke kula da ayyukan 'yan Democrat a Amirka ya gaya wa jaridar cewa: "Ba wai kawai batun zaɓen da aka yi a kotun ba ne, ko kuma zaɓen da aka yi na ƙarshe, ko kuma amincewar Kavanaugh a matsayin alƙali a Kotun Koli, amma kuma yadda jam'iyyar Republican ta bi da wannan batun da kuma yadda ta bi da matar".
