Wani sabon ƙulla na YoGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin ɗari na waɗanda suka shiga cikin ƙulla sun amince da shaidar Ford, kuma kashi 35 cikin ɗari sun amince da shaidar Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya sa'ad da yake ba da shaida, kuma kashi 30 cikin ɗari sun ce Ford ya yi ƙarya sa'ad da yake ba da shaida.
Jaridar Guardian ta ce, bayan da Flake ya yi zargin, hukumar FBI tana binciken abin da Ford da Deborah Ramirez suka faɗa.
