Ramirez ya ce Kavanaugh ya nuna masa batsa a lokacin da yake makaranta a Yale a shekara ta 1980.
Masu tsara dandalin World Wide Web suna son su kafa dandalin da zai yi gasa da Google da kuma Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya ƙirƙiri Intane, yana shirin kafa wani dandalin sadarwa da zai yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon, da kuma Google.
Wani sabon aikin da aka yi, mai suna Inrupt, wani shiri ne da ake son a ci gaba da shi bayan da aka daina aikin Solid da Berner-Lee ya yi.
Shafin Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓan inda za su adana abubuwan da suke da shi kuma su zaɓi saƙon da suke so mutane su gani.
A wata hira da aka yi da jaridar Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa'azin cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "ta fi kowa".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da wannan dandalin.
"Wannan albishiri ne mai ban sha'awa".
Wannan shirin zai yi amfani da fasahar Solid don ba da damar mutane su gina nasu "wurin ajiya na kan layi" ko kuma POD.
Wannan tsarin zai iya adana bayanai, ayyuka, kalanda, waƙoƙi, da kuma wasu bayanai na sirri da na aiki.
Kamar dai an haɗa Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify a lokaci guda.
Wani abu na musamman game da wannan tsarin shi ne, mai amfani yana da 'yancin ya zaɓi waɗanda za su iya ganin saƙon da yake so.
Kamfanin ya ce wannan shirin "za su ƙarfafa mutane ta wurin yin amfani da saƙo".
Shugaban kamfanin John Bruce ya ce manufarmu a Inrupt ita ce samar da kayayyaki, hanyoyin da fasaha da suka dace don tabbatar da cewa kowa zai iya samun Solid.
A yanzu, Berners-Lee da Bruce da kuma wasu masu fasaha da suka ba da kansu suna aiki a kamfanin, har da masu tsaro da aka saya daga kamfanin IBM da kuma wasu da suka yi aiki a kamfanin.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kwamfuta a duniya sun sami damar tsara shirye-shiryensu ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da abokansa ba sa tattaunawa da "masu mallakar Facebook da Google game da ko za su yi gyara na dindindin da zai sa a daina yin amfani da su a wani lokaci.
"Ba ma neman izininsu".
A cikin wani labarin da aka wallafa a shafin Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "burin Inrupt shi ne samar da damar kasuwanci da kuma tasirin muhalli don kare fasahar da kuma ingancin sabon software daga wannan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja yadda ake amfani da Intane sa'ad da ya kafa dandalinsa na Intane a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya yi magana a kan batun haɗin kan masu tsara shirye-shiryen Intane.
Ko da bayan ya kafa Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance mai shi da kuma darektan World Wide Web, Web Foundation da kuma makarantar Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabon tsarin", in ji Berners-Lee.
