Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su 'ji matsin lamba' daga 'yan adawa da EU - kamar yadda ɗaya daga cikin masu ba Theresa May shawara ya ce ya kamata a yi wa tattaunawar da EU.
Peter Bone, wani dan siyasa mai goyon baya, ya shaida wa jama'a a Birmingham cewa da Birtaniya ta 'fita' a yanzu idan Farage ya kasance Sakatare a tattaunawar Brexit.
Amma matsalar da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen mayar da yankunan da aka raba su da yawa ta nuna cewa masu adawa da Brexit sun sa ta shiga wasu zanga-zangar adawa da Brexit a cikin birni.
Shugaban ya yi kokarin ganin cewa shirinsa na neman 'yancin kai daga kasar ya yi daidai da na masu goyon bayan Brexit, masu neman shiga Tarayyar Turai da kuma kungiyar Tarayyar Turai.
'Yan jam'iyyar sun ce za su ci gaba da kokarin shiga yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da adawa - kuma su tilasta wa 'yan adawar EU da Labor su zabi tsakanin abin da suke bayarwa da kuma 'rashin tsari'.
Mista Bone ya shaida wa wani taro mai taken Fita yana nufin Fita daga Solihull cewa yana son 'fitowa kan masu adawa da yarjejeniyar Brexit'.
Ya kuma ce Farage ya kamata ya sa hannu kuma a ba shi aikin tattaunawa da Brussels.
'Da a ce haka suke, da mun zo nan,' in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: 'Ina goyon bayan Brexit amma muna son mu yi adawa da masu adawa da yarjejeniyar Brexit.'
Da yake ba da hujja game da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙi ba domin mu zama bayi.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.'
Bone ya musanta cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya sauya tun bayan zaben 2016: 'Ba gaskiya ba ne cewa 'yan Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su ci gaba da zama.'
'Yar'uwar Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns ma tana wajen, tana gaya wa manema labarai: 'Ina ce muku: Firayim Minista, ku saurari mutane.
'Mutanen ba sa son zama a cikin EU, 'Yan adawa ba za su yarda da hakan ba, kuma ba su son jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutuka da ke neman mu yi zabe.
Ku bar EU ku saurari mutane.'
Ga Mrs. May, ta daɗa: 'Manyan mutane kamar firaminista suna cika aikinsu idan sun cika alkawarinsu.'
Farage ya gaya wa masu sauraro a taron cewa dole ne a 'tilasta' 'yan siyasa idan sun kasance marasa aminci ga zaben 2016.
Yanzu batun gaskiya ne tsakaninmu - mutane - da kuma jam'iyyarmu ta siyasa,' in ji shi.
'Suna ƙoƙarin su yi rashin gaskiya game da Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don mu gaya musu cewa 'ba za mu bari ku yi haka ba'.'
A cikin saƙo ga wannan rukunin masu sha'awar, ya daɗa cewa: 'Ina so ku matsa wa 'yan siyasa, waɗanda ba su da tabbaci game da Brexit.
'Muna kira ga rundunar 'yan siyasa da suka yi yaƙi dominmu game da Brexit kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama Ƙasar Ingila mai 'yanci da kuma alfahari.'
A yanzu, 'yan takarar EU sun wuce Birmingham kafin su yi taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Masu adawa da Brexit da dama sun yi wa 'yan adawa da Brexit alama a kan allon tallace-tallace da suka kafa kungiyar a wannan makon.
A lokacin da aka buɗe taron, wani ɗan jam'iyyar Labour mai suna Lord Adonis ya yi wa 'yan Conservatives ba'a game da matsalar tsaro da suka fuskanta da tsarin kwamfutarsu.
'Waɗannan mutane ne da ke gaya mana cewa za su iya kafa tsarin IT a cikin ƙasar da kuma fasahar gaba ɗaya a Kanada ciki har da, iyakar da ba ta da iyaka, sayar da kyauta ba tare da iyaka a Ireland ba,' in ji shi.
'Wannan abin dariya ne.
Babu abin da ya fi Brexit kyau,' in ji shi.
Warren yana son ya "yi tunani sosai" game da zaɓen shugaban ƙasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta "yi tunani sosai game da neman shugabanci" bayan zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat na Massachusetts ya yi magana game da makomarsa a wani taro da aka yi a yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, wanda ya saba adawa da Shugaba Donald Trump, yana fatan sake zabarsa a watan Nuwamba a kan GOP jihar Rep. Geoff Diehl wanda ya kasance abokin shugaban yakin neman zaben Trump a shekarar 2016 a Massachusetts.
An yi zaton zai iya yin hamayya da Trump a shekarar 2020
Aikin da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne taronsa na 36 da dan majalisa ya yi ta amfani da tsarin tambayoyi da amsoshi tun lokacin da Trump ya fara aiki.
Wani mai sauraro ya tambaye shi ko yana son ya yi kamfen don ya zama shugaban ƙasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da "mahaifiyata za ta tafi Washington ta gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, har da babban mata".
An kama wani saboda harbin da ya kashe dan wasan LSU Sims
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, La., sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa an kama wani da ake zargin cewa ɗan bindiga ne wanda ya harbe kuma ya kashe dan wasan LSU Sims a ranar Juma'a.
'Yan sandan Baton Rouge sun sanar da kamawar Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, da karfe 11 na safe.
Ya fitar da bidiyo na abin da ya faru a ranar Juma'a, yana neman taimako don gano mutumin da aka gani a bidiyon.
Sims, ɗan shekara 20, an kashe shi da bindiga kusa da Jami'ar Kudancin Amirka a ranar Jumma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya ji rauni a kai kuma daga baya ya mutu, "in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul ga manema labarai a ranar Asabar, a 247 Sports.
Wayde ya shiga don ya kāre abokin aikinsa kuma Simpson ya kashe shi da bindiga.
An yi wa Simpson tambayoyi kuma ya yarda cewa yana wurin, yana da makami, kuma ya yarda cewa wannan shi ne yadda ya kashe Wayde Sims da bindiga.
An kama Simpson ba tare da ya ƙi ba kuma aka tsare shi a Sashen 'Yan Sanda na East Baton Rouge.
Matashin mai kafa 6 da ya girma a Baton Rouge, Sims ya buga wasanni 32 kuma ya fara wasanni 10 a kakar wasa ta bara tare da yin matsakaicin minti 17.4, ci 5.6 da kuma samun dama 2.9 a kowane wasa.
Gasar tseren mota ta Rasha: Lewis Hamilton yana da damar lashe gasar cin kofin duniya ta wajen cin Sebastian Vettel bisa ga dokokin gasar
Ya bayyana a fili bayan da Valtteri Bottas ya doke Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar a wasan shiga na biyu cewa dokokin Mercedes za su yi tasiri a kan sakamakon wasan karshe.
