Rana ce mai wuya domin Valtteri ya yi aiki mai kyau a ƙarshen mako kuma ya kasance ƙwararre sosai.
Wannan tawagar ta yi aiki mai girma don samun nasara biyu", in ji Hamilton.
Yin Alamar Jiki Ba Hanya Ce Mai Kyau Ba
Shugaba Donald Trump ya soki Sanata Dianne Feinstein a wani taro a ranar Asabar saboda ta nace cewa ba ta fitar da wata takarda daga Christine Blasey Ford ba da ke tuhumar Babban Kotun Brett Kavanaugh kan laifin lalata.
A wani jawabi da ya ba da a wani taro a West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar da Ford ya bayar a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa ba, amma ya ce abin da ke faruwa a Majalisar Dattijai ya nuna cewa mutane "masu mugunta ne, masu mugunta, da kuma masu ƙarya".
"Abu daya da zai iya faruwa kuma mafi kyau da zai iya faruwa a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan a majalisar dattijai shi ne, idan ka ga fushi, idan ka ga mutane masu zalunci da fushi da mugunta da kuma karya", in ji shi.
"Ka kalli abin da ya faru a cikin akwatin, sai ka ji wani ya ce, "Ai, ban yi hakan ba.
Ban yi hakan ba".
Ka Tuna da Wannan?
Dianne Feistein, kai ne ka bayyana su?
Ka tuna da amsar da ya bayar... kai ne ka yi magana a fili - "iii, iiii, menene?
A'a, ba haka ba ne.
Ban faɗa ba".
To, bari mu ce haka.
"Mun bayyana shi a fili?... A'a, ba mu ba", in ji Trump a cikin jawabinsa, wanda ya nuna cewa yana magana ne game da majalisar dattawa.
An aika wa Feinstein takarda da ta ba da cikakken bayani game da shari'ar Kavanaugh da Ford a watan Yuli da ya gabata, kuma an bayyana batun a watan Satumba - amma Feinstein ya musanta cewa ofishinsa ne ya yi wannan fashin.
"Ban ɓoye kome ba game da batun da ya zo da Mr. Ford, ban bayyana shi ba", in ji Feinstein ga Kwamitin Majalisar Dattawa, kamar yadda jaridar The Hill ta ruwaito.
"An gaya mini cewa ya kamata na riƙe wannan asirin kuma na yi hakan".
Wannan ƙin yarda bai faranta wa shugaban ƙasa rai ba, wanda ya yi magana a taron ranar Asabar: "Ka gaya mini, wannan ba hanya ce mai kyau ta yin magana ta wurin nuna jiki ba.
Wataƙila ba haka ba ne, amma wannan ita ce hanyar magana ta jiki mafi muni da na taɓa gani".
A cikin ci gaba da kare wanda aka nada a Kotun Koli, wanda ake zargi da laifin lalata da mata uku, shugaban ya ce 'yan Democrat suna amfani da wannan bayanin don cimma burinsu.
"Manufarsu ita ce su dawo da iko ta kowace hanya.
Ka san cewa mutanen nan mugaye ne, masu zalunci, da ba su damu da wanda suke cutarwa ba domin suna son su mallaki iko", in ji shugaban, in ji jaridar Mediaite.
Game da Gasar Kwallon Kafa: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a wasan da suka yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun rama wannan zargi ne lokacin da suka doke Belfast Giants da ci 5 da 3 a wasan sake dawowa a filin wasan su ranar Asabar da ta gabata.
A farkon wasan, 'yan wasan Belfast Giants sun ci kwallaye biyu da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Amma Dundee sun ci kwallaye biyu da Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie, kuma Dwyer na Belfast Giants ya sake kai wa 'yan wasansa kwallo.
Francois Bouchard ya ci kwallo da ya daidaita ƙwallo, sai kuma Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci biyu da suka sa Dundee Stars ta ci.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da Adam Keefe ya ci nasara a gasar Elite League a kakar, wanda ya zo daga baya ya ci Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Jumma'a da dare.
Wannan shi ne karo na huɗu da 'yan wasan suka ci nasara a gasar, kuma Giants sun ci nasara a wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya ci ƙwallo na farko a minti na huɗu da minti 3:35 ta Kendall McFaull, kuma David Rutherford ya ci na biyu daga Beauvillier da minti huɗu daga ƙwallo na farko.
A lokacin da aka fara wasa, Sullivan ya sake dawo da 'yan wasan a 13:10 na dare, kafin Matt Marquardt ya ba Cownie damar cin kwallo wanda ya sa aka daidaita a 15:16 na dare.
Dwyer ya ƙarfafa Giants a farkon hutu yayin da ya zira kwallaye na biyu a wasan daren a ƙarshen farkon.
Ƙungiyar Dundee da ke gida ta yi wani abu kuma Bouchard ya ci kwallo mai ƙarfi a minti 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun yi wasa mai kyau a wasan da suka buga wa Nielsen wanda ya zira kwallaye na Dundee wanda ya ba da jagoranci a karon farko a ƙarshen rabin wasan kuma ya kara da cewa ya ci kwallaye biyar a wasan.
Giants, da suka ci wasanni huɗu cikin biyar na gasar, suna shirin yin wasa da Milton Keynes a wasan da za a yi a ranar Jumma'a.
Mataimakin Matukin Jirgin Ya Mutu Yayin da Yake Taimaka wa Daruruwan Matattara Su Tsere
An yaba wa mataimakin matukin jirgi a Indonesia a matsayin jarumi bayan ya mutu domin ya taimaki jirgin sama mai ɗauke da ɗarurruwan mutane ya sauka lafiya.
Fiye da mutane 800 sun mutu kuma ba a san ko su wanene ba bayan girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, ta jawo tsunami.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta ci gaba a yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun yi hasarar birnin Palu.
Yayin da abokansa suka gudu domin su ceci rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung mai shekara 21 ya ki barin wurin aikinsa a kan wani dandamali mai girgiza a filin jirgin saman Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Palu.
Ya kasance don ya taimaki jirgin Batik Air Flight 6321, da ke tashi daga filin jirgin sama a lokacin
Sai suka yi tsalle daga saman wannan hasumiya da suke ganin za ta rushe.
Daga baya ya mutu a asibiti.
Kakakin kamfanin jirgin sama na Indonesiya, Yohannes Sirait ya ce wannan shawarar ta ceci daruruwan rayuka, in ji ABC News Australia.
Mun yi jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu daga Balikpapan, Kalimantan, don mu kai shi wani asibiti mai kyau a wani birni.
Abin baƙin ciki, ya mutu da safiyar yau kafin jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu ya isa Palu.
"Mun yi baƙin ciki sosai da muka ji haka", in ji shi.
A yanzu, hukumomi na tsoron cewa adadin mutanen da za su mutu zai iya kaiwa dubbai kuma sashen kula da bala'i na kasar ya ce yana da wuya a kai ga garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong.
"An yi imanin cewa adadin waɗanda suka mutu yana ƙaruwa yayin da wasu gawawwakin har yanzu suna ƙarƙashin shara kuma ba a haɗa yawancin su don a duba su ba", in ji mai magana da yawun ƙungiyar, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Ruwa mai tsawon kafa shida ya lalata Palu kuma za a yi jana'izar waɗanda suka mutu a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna kawo taimako da kuma kayayyaki.
Risa Kusuma, wata mata 'yar shekara 35, ta gaya wa Sky News: Kowane minti ana kawo gawawwakin mutane a motar asibiti.
Ba a samun ruwa mai tsabta da sauƙi.
Ana yin sata a dukan ƙananan kasuwanni.
Jan Gelfand, shugaban Hukumar Ceto ta Duniya a Indonesia, ya gaya wa CNN: "Ceto ta Duniya ta Indonesia tana gaggauta zuwa wajen waɗanda suka tsira amma ba mu san abin da za ta samu a wurin ba.
Wannan matsalar ta riga ta kasance, amma za ta iya ƙaruwa.
Shugaban ƙasar Indonesiya Joko Widodo ya ziyarci birnin Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin ƙasar: "Ina roƙonku ku yi aiki dare da rana don ku kammala dukan aikin da ya shafi kwashe mutane.
Kana shirye ka yi hakan?" in ji CNN.
A farkon wannan shekarar, girgizar kasa ta afkawa Indonesia a Lombok, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 550.
Hadarin jirgin sama a Micronesia: Kamfanin jiragen sama na Air Niugini ya sanar da cewa har yanzu babu wanda ya rasa ransa bayan jirgin ya fadi cikin ruwa
Kamfanin, wanda shi ne mai jirgin da ya yi hatsari a tekun Pacific, ya ce har yanzu ba a gano wanda ya yi hatsarin ba, bayan da ya ce an ceto duk fasinjojin jirgin ne a lokacin da jirgin ya nutse.
Kamfanin jiragen sama na Air Niugini ya sanar da cewa a ranar Asabar da rana, an gano cewa an rasa wani ɗan asalin ƙasar.
Ya ce a yanzu haka, yana aiki tare da hukumomin tsaro, da na kiwon lafiya da kuma masu bincike a kan neman mutumin da ya ɓace.
Kamfanin ba ya amsa duk wani bayani da ya samu game da mutumin da aka rasa, kamar shekarunsa ko kuma ƙasarsa.
Masu jirgin ruwa a yankin sun yi gaggawar ceton mutane bayan jirgin ya fadi a cikin ruwa yayin da yake shirin sauka a filin jirgin saman tsibirin Chuuk.
Wasu hukumomi sun sanar da cewa an kai mutane bakwai asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce ba a sallami fasinjoji shida daga asibiti ba a ranar Litinin, amma duk suna samun sauki.
Har yanzu ba a san ainihin dalilin da ya sa hatsarin ya faru ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da kuma rundunar sojin ruwa na Amirka sun ce jirgin ya fadi a cikin ruwa sa'ad da yake gab da sauka a filin jirgin sama.
Wasu Shaidu sun ɗauka cewa jirgin ya tsallaka hanya.
Wani matukin jirgin sama mai suna Bill Jaynes ya ce wannan jirgin yana tashi da wuri sosai.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu sun tsere cikin ruwa mai yawa har zuwa cinya zuwa inda jirgin yake nitsewa.
Ya ce ma'aikatan jirgin suna nuna baƙar fata kuma suna ihu, kuma ya ce ya ji rauni kaɗan a kai.
Rundunar Sojan Ruwa ta Amirka ta ce masu aikin jirgin ruwa da suke aiki a wurin da ake gyara jirgin ruwa sun taimaka sosai wajen ceton mutane ta wajen kai su bakin teku da jirgin ruwa kafin jirgin ya nutse a cikin ruwa na kusan mita 30.
Bayanai daga Cibiyar Tsaron Jiragen Sama sun nuna cewa mutane 111 sun mutu a hadarin jirgin sama da aka yi rajista a PNG a cikin shekaru 20 da suka gabata amma babu wanda ya shafi Air Niugini.
Masana sun ba da jerin abubuwan da suka faru kafin a ƙona mace da rai
Mai gabatar da kara ya dakatar da shari'ar ranar Asabar na wani mutum da ake zargi da ƙona wata mata a Mississippi a 2014.
Wani mai bincike na Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amirka, Paul Rowlett ya ba da shaida na sa'o'i da yawa a matsayin gwani a bincike.
Ya bayyana wa kotu yadda ya yi amfani da wayoyin salula don ya gano tafiyar mai laifi mai shekara 29 mai suna Quinton Tellis da kuma mai shekara 19 mai suna Jessica Chambers, a daren da suka mutu.
Rowlett ta ce ta samu bayanai game da wurin daga wayoyin salula da dama da suka nuna cewa Tellis yana tare da Chambers a daren da ya mutu, wanda ya sabawa abin da ta ce a baya, Clarion Ledger ya ce.
Bayan da suka nuna cewa tana da wayar Chambers a lokacin da take tare da abokinta Michael Sanford, 'yan sanda suka je su nemi Sanford.
Sanford ya shaida cewa a ranar Asabar ba ya cikin gari.
Sa'ad da aka tambayi lauya ko Tellis ya yi gaskiya game da abin da ya ce ya yi a motar Sanford a daren, Sanford ya ce "ƙarya ce, domin motata tana Nashville a lokacin".
Wani abin da ba a yarda da shi ba shi ne cewa Tellis ya ce ya san Chambers kusan makonni biyu bayan mutuwarsa.
Bayanan da aka samu daga wayoyin salula sun nuna cewa sun san juna ne kawai na mako guda.
Rowlett ta ce jim kadan bayan mutuwar Chambers, Tellis ya goge bayanan Chambers, da yawa suna kira da sunansa daga wayarta.
Hale ya ce: "An cire shi daga rayuwarsa.
Ana sa ran mai hamayya zai ba da hujjojinsa na ƙarshe a ranar Lahadi.
Alƙalin ya ce yana sa rai cewa za a kai karar kotu a ranar.
High Breed: Menene marijuana na hip-hop?
Wasu mawaƙa uku na wiwi suna tunanin canja ra'ayin da ke cewa wiwi yana da lahani ta wajen saka saƙo mai ƙarfafawa a cikin waƙoƙinsu.
High Breed, wani rukunin mawaƙa daga birnin Bristol, sun ce hip hop ya daina magana game da siyasa da kuma magance matsalolinmu na yau da kullum.
Manufar wannan rukunin ita ce ta mai da hankali ga yadda marijuana take sa mutane su yi abubuwa.
Masu kida kamar su The Fugees da Common sun ga sake farfadowa a Birtaniya ta hanyar mawaƙa kamar su Akala da Lowkey.
Wani baƙar fata?!
Wani mai kula da yara a New York ya tuhumi wasu ma'aurata da aika saƙon "na wariyar launin fata"
Wani mai kula da yara a New York ya tuhumi wata iyali da aika saƙon wariyar launin fata bayan da ta karɓi saƙo da ba a san ko wane ne ba daga mahaifiyar da ke gunaguni cewa ita "babbar baƙar fata ce".
Ma'auratan sun ce wannan "nau'i ne na sata".
Lynsey Plasco-Flaxman, mahaifiyar yara biyu, ta nuna takaicinta bayan ta gano cewa sabuwar mai kula da yara, Giselle Maurice, baƙar fata ce a ranar fara aiki a shekarar 2016.
"WANI mutum mai ƙiyayya", in ji Mrs. Plasco-Flaxmanto a wasiƙa zuwa ga mijinta.
Maimakon ta aika wa mijinta, ta aika wa Uwargida Maurice sau biyu.
Da suka fahimci laifinsa, "marasa aminci" Plasco-Flaxm suka kori 'Yar'uwa Maurice, suna cewa tsohon mai kula da su, ɗan Afirka-Amurka, ya yi mugun aiki kuma a maimakon haka suna sa rai za su sami wani daga Philippines, in ji New York Post.
An biya Maurice kuɗin aikinsa na rana ɗaya kuma aka tura shi gida a motar Uber.
Yanzu, Maurice yana neman biyan kuɗin aikinsa, kuma yana neman $350 a rana na watanni shida, aikin da ya yi kafin wannan yarjejeniya.
"Ina so in nuna musu, ba ku aikata abubuwa haka ba", in ji shi ga Jaridar Post ta Jumma'a, ya daɗa cewa "Na san cewa nuna bambanci ne".
Waɗannan biyun sun kāre kansu daga zargin nuna bambanci, suna cewa ya dace a kori Maurice, domin suna tsoron kada su amince da shi idan ya yi abin da bai dace ba.
"Matata ta aika masa da wani abu da ba ta son ta faɗa.
Ba ya son kai.
Ba mu nuna bambanci ba", in ji Joel Plasco ga Post.
"Amma za ka iya ba da yaranka ga mutumin da ka yi wa mugunta ba da saninsa ba?
Ɗanka da aka haifa?
Ku mutane".
Da yake kwatanta wannan shari'ar da "shan kuɗi", Plasco ya ce matarsa ta yi ciki watanni biyu ne kawai kuma tana "cikin mawuyacin hali".
"Za ka fita ka yi yaƙi da mutumin da yake cikin irin wannan yanayin?
